\",null,{\"children\":\"Communicate with you about opportunities and updates\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Comply with legal and regulatory requirements\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display text-display-sm text-soft-gold mb-4\",\"children\":\"How we store your data\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Your data is stored securely in accordance with UK GDPR requirements. We retain personal data only for as long as necessary for the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display text-display-sm text-soft-gold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Your rights\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Access the personal data we hold about you\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Request correction of inaccurate data\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Request deletion of your data\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Object to processing of your data\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Request data portability\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display text-display-sm text-soft-gold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Contact us\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"If you have questions about this privacy policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us at\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"mailto:hello@medibee-recruitment.co.uk\",\"className\":\"text-rich-gold hover:text-soft-gold underline\",\"children\":\"hello@medibee-recruitment.co.uk\"}],\".\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display text-display-sm text-soft-gold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Complaints\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"If you are not satisfied with how